# Public URL of THIS API (no trailing slash). Required on Render/VPS so /uploads/... links work from the Vercel frontend.
# Example: https://your-backend.onrender.com
# Render often sets RENDER_EXTERNAL_URL automatically; you can also set PUBLIC_API_URL explicitly.
